      • nodesToApplyRulesTo

        public List<SNode> nodesToApplyRulesTo​(SNode attributedNode)
        Returns the list of all node attributes with the attributedNode added as the last. The rules applicable to earlier attributes can be amended by the rules applicable to attributes added later. At some point a rule may declare to "supercede" the rules that follow, which then become obsolete. This logic is in sync with the editor's policy for overriding editor cells using attributes.
        Parameters:
        attributedNode -
